recipe.label: Gluten-Free Coconut Curry Laksa
ingredientLines: * 150 gram rice noodle, soaked for 5 minute in hot water
* 3 cup chicken broth (can use vegetable broth, shrimp broth)
* 270 ml coconut milk (1 can, or about 1 cup)
* 3 stalk lemongrass, beaten and chopped in 1/2 so that they release
* 2 to 3 kaffir lime leaf, remove the stem to release flavour
* 2 quartered lime (i used key lime )- optional
* 2 hard boiled egg, peeled and sliced in 1/2 - optional
* handful mung bean (bean sprout), cut in 1/2 - optional
* handful cilantro (coriander or vietnamese coriander called daun
* chili sambal sauce a desired - optional
